<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 20:07:28 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美国与以色列对伊朗的袭击保持距离，专注于缓和局势</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-19/ty-article/.premium/u-s-distances-itself-from-israels-strike-in-iran-focusing-on-deescalation-efforts/0000018e-f6d3-d87e-a58e-f7f3f7ab0000</link><description>据报道，以色列周五早上袭击了伊朗境内的目标后，美国很快否认参与了这些事件。意大利七国集团峰会期间，布林肯强调美国对以色列国防的承诺，并宣布七国集团联合制裁伊朗武器工业</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 17:03:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-19/ty-article/.premium/u-s-distances-itself-from-israels-strike-in-iran-focusing-on-deescalation-efforts/0000018e-f6d3-d87e-a58e-f7f3f7ab0000</guid></item><item><title>西方外交官认为以色列对伊朗的反应是相称的，不会导致局势升级</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-19/ty-article/.premium/western-diplomats-believe-israeli-response-to-iran-is-proportionate-wont-escalate-region/0000018e-f6aa-d87e-a58e-f7aaf1060000</link><description>几位外交官表示，他们的国家最近几天与以色列就打击伊朗问题举行了会谈，试图防止冲突升级。一位外交官表示，危险尚未过去，“但仍有谨慎乐观的空间”</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 17:02:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-19/ty-article/.premium/western-diplomats-believe-israeli-response-to-iran-is-proportionate-wont-escalate-region/0000018e-f6aa-d87e-a58e-f7aaf1060000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 196 天：世界敦促以色列和伊朗在伊斯法罕袭击后缓和紧张局势</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-04-19/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-196-world-urges-israel-iran-to-de-escalate-after-isfahan-strike/0000018e-f730-df38-abbf-ffb82d050000</link><description>国际媒体报道，以色列袭击了伊朗城市伊斯法罕附近的空军基地 ■ 官方媒体报道，伊朗高级官员称袭击没有造成任何损害，没有计划立即进行报复 ■ 美国、欧盟制裁以色列极右活动人士和非政府组织 ■ 评级机构标准普尔全球评级下调以色列的长期评级 ■ 美国否决了联合国安理会给予巴勒斯坦权力机构正式成员地位的提议 ■ 战争结束 196 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 16:38:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-04-19/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-196-world-urges-israel-iran-to-de-escalate-after-isfahan-strike/0000018e-f730-df38-abbf-ffb82d050000</guid></item><item><title>美国和欧盟制裁以色列著名极右活动人士和为先前受制裁的西岸定居者筹款的非政府组织</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-19/ty-article/.premium/u-s-eu-sanction-settler-leaders-ngos-that-fundraised-for-sanctioned-settlers/0000018e-f6a2-d79f-a98e-f7a6408f0000</link><description>在约旦河西岸暴力升级的背景下，美国宣布对以色列极右翼人士和团体实施新的制裁，特别是两个极右翼非政府组织，因为它们为此前受到美国制裁的定居者筹款。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 15:23:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-19/ty-article/.premium/u-s-eu-sanction-settler-leaders-ngos-that-fundraised-for-sanctioned-settlers/0000018e-f6a2-d79f-a98e-f7a6408f0000</guid></item><item><title>战争看不到结束的迹象，以色列的评级下调可能只是一个开始</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-19/ty-article/.premium/with-no-end-to-the-war-in-sight-israels-rating-downgrade-could-just-be-the-beginning/0000018e-f62e-df38-abbf-feae8dea0000</link><description>标准普尔的决定暴露了人们真正的担忧，即降级将改变投资者对以色列经济的情绪。如果以色列有一位能够在战时内阁内部做出经济决策的专业财政部长，这将会有所帮助</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 14:38:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-19/ty-article/.premium/with-no-end-to-the-war-in-sight-israels-rating-downgrade-could-just-be-the-beginning/0000018e-f62e-df38-abbf-feae8dea0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列对伊斯法罕的无声打击表明内塔尼亚胡对伊朗和加沙没有战略</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-19/ty-article/.premium/israels-muted-strike-on-isfahan-shows-netanyahu-has-no-strategy-on-iran-as-well-as-gaza/0000018e-f623-df38-abbf-feab83690000</link><description>以色列对伊斯法罕的平淡打击至多只是一种临时措施，一种占位性措施。这是内塔尼亚胡下令的，他以谈论伊朗威胁为职业，但当关键时刻到来时，他无话可说或提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 12:54:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-19/ty-article/.premium/israels-muted-strike-on-isfahan-shows-netanyahu-has-no-strategy-on-iran-as-well-as-gaza/0000018e-f623-df38-abbf-feab83690000</guid></item><item><title>以色列对伊朗袭击的反应影响了拉法行动的合法性</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-19/ty-article/.premium/israels-response-to-iranian-attack-impacts-legitimacy-of-an-operation-in-rafah/0000018e-f5c4-d87e-a58e-f5e6cf2f0000</link><description>据报道，埃及和巴勒斯坦权力机构已经接受以色列将进入拉法的事实，并开始准备吸纳流离失所者和管理民政。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 11:21:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-19/ty-article/.premium/israels-response-to-iranian-attack-impacts-legitimacy-of-an-operation-in-rafah/0000018e-f5c4-d87e-a58e-f5e6cf2f0000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗给了内塔尼亚胡前所未有的机会，但他是错失机会的冠军</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-19/ty-article/.premium/iran-gave-netanyahu-an-unprecedented-opportunity-but-hes-a-pro-at-missing-opportunities/0000018e-f2b0-d240-a19f-f6b31d610000</link><description>伊朗一周前的袭击给了以色列重新获得西方世界青睐的机会。以色列的克制会被证明是审慎的吗？ ■ 事情变得越来越清楚：战争结束前人质不会返回 ■ 甘茨继续与内塔尼亚胡合作 ■ 极右翼分子斯莫特里奇遭遇不那么即时的因果报应</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 10:24:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-19/ty-article/.premium/iran-gave-netanyahu-an-unprecedented-opportunity-but-hes-a-pro-at-missing-opportunities/0000018e-f2b0-d240-a19f-f6b31d610000</guid></item><item><title>报道：以色列对伊朗的袭击目标是核设施附近的防空雷达站</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-19/ty-article-live/reports-say-israel-attacked-site-in-iran-explosions-heard-in-isfahan/0000018e-f484-daad-a3de-febf4f4e0000</link><description>人质家属抗议要求释放人质；封锁主要高速公路 ■ 以色列官员向《华盛顿邮报》证实对伊朗进行空袭 ■ 据《纽约时报》报道，三名伊朗官员称袭击袭击了伊朗西部伊斯法罕附近的军事基地 ■ 美国对伊朗无人机计划、钢铁、汽车行业实施新制裁 ■ 欧盟和美国对定居者领导人和非政府组织实施制裁 ■ 标准普尔下调以色列信用评级</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 04:17:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-19/ty-article-live/reports-say-israel-attacked-site-in-iran-explosions-heard-in-isfahan/0000018e-f484-daad-a3de-febf4f4e0000</guid></item><item><title>《纽约时报》报道伊朗空军基地在以色列袭击中遭到袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/iran/2024-04-19/ty-article/israeli-missiles-hit-a-site-in-iran-abc-news-reports-iran-suspends-flights-above-cities/0000018e-f42c-daad-a3de-fe3f48450000</link><description>伊朗电视台称，在宣布防空系统已启动后，核设施在报道中的袭击中未受损</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 03:15:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/iran/2024-04-19/ty-article/israeli-missiles-hit-a-site-in-iran-abc-news-reports-iran-suspends-flights-above-cities/0000018e-f42c-daad-a3de-fe3f48450000</guid></item><item><title>数百人在威尼斯双年展以色列馆外抗议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/leisure/2024-04-19/ty-article/.premium/hundreds-protest-outside-israeli-pavilion-at-venice-biennale/0000018e-f3b2-df38-abbf-ffbab06f0000</link><description>在这场著名的艺术活动中，亲巴勒斯坦抗议者指责以色列实施种族灭绝，而活动人士则在城市各处悬挂了 40 件巴勒斯坦艺术家的作品</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 00:27:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/leisure/2024-04-19/ty-article/.premium/hundreds-protest-outside-israeli-pavilion-at-venice-biennale/0000018e-f3b2-df38-abbf-ffbab06f0000</guid></item><item><title>标准普尔下调以色列信用评级，理由是与伊朗的军事升级风险</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/business/economy-finance/2024-04-19/ty-article/s-p-says-israels-long-term-credit-outlook-negative-iran-tensions-increasing-risk/0000018e-f38b-d240-a19f-f78b9f0b0000</link><description>负面展望反映了以色列与哈马斯战争以及与真主党或伊朗的对抗可能对以色列经济的影响超过该机构目前预期的风险</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 23:38:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/business/economy-finance/2024-04-19/ty-article/s-p-says-israels-long-term-credit-outlook-negative-iran-tensions-increasing-risk/0000018e-f38b-d240-a19f-f78b9f0b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列招标建造拥有 1,000 多套住房的东耶路撒冷新犹太社区</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-bids-new-jewish-neighborhood-in-east-jerusalem-with-over-1-000-housing-units/0000018e-f2bf-d87e-a58e-f7bf7adf0000</link><description>以色列土地管理局周三发出了该社区建设投标邀请，距地区规划界批准仅三个月——与其他类似项目相比，时间非常短</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 20:27:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-bids-new-jewish-neighborhood-in-east-jerusalem-with-over-1-000-housing-units/0000018e-f2bf-d87e-a58e-f7bf7adf0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列-哈马斯战争如何将这个安静的犹太郊区变成战区</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/how-the-israel-hamas-war-turned-this-quiet-jewish-suburb-into-a-battle-zone/0000018e-ebda-d7e3-a9bf-ffffa62a0000</link><description>纽约郊区蒂内克是犹太人聚居的地方，已成为加沙战争导致犹太穆斯林紧张关系的导火索。一位相关的当地拉比表示，“有一种感觉，这超出了通常的反以色列活动”，而另一位拉比则称该镇的抗议活动是“公然的恐吓”</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 20:23:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/how-the-israel-hamas-war-turned-this-quiet-jewish-suburb-into-a-battle-zone/0000018e-ebda-d7e3-a9bf-ffffa62a0000</guid></item><item><title>“一位澳大利亚朋友告诉我：如果发生核战争，就来这里重建家园”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/an-aussie-friend-told-me-if-theres-nuclear-war-come-here-and-rebuild-yourselves/0000018e-f2b6-d240-a19f-f6b7da3b0000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：一名澳大利亚移民在战争期间拒绝离开以色列，因为“这就是这里的生活”，一名军官在六个月的预备役后重新适应文明社会</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 20:08:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/an-aussie-friend-told-me-if-theres-nuclear-war-come-here-and-rebuild-yourselves/0000018e-f2b6-d240-a19f-f6b7da3b0000</guid></item><item><title>被伊朗导弹击伤的 7 岁贝都因女孩的家人为她祈祷，并为她提供庇护所</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/family-of-7-year-old-bedouin-girl-wounded-by-iranian-missile-pray-for-her-and-shelters/0000018e-f24b-d620-abaf-f26b20120000</link><description>女孩受伤后的几天里，只有一名内阁部长探望过她的家人。尽管她因村庄没有避难所而受伤，正在为生命而战，但以色列国防军和政府仍在吹嘘军队防空系统的成功</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 20:00:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/family-of-7-year-old-bedouin-girl-wounded-by-iranian-missile-pray-for-her-and-shelters/0000018e-f24b-d620-abaf-f26b20120000</guid></item><item><title>事实上，威尼斯双年展上有一个以色列展览</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/actually-there-is-an-israeli-exhibit-at-the-venice-biennale/0000018e-f153-ddac-a59e-f9db55e90000</link><description>露丝·帕蒂尔（Ruth Patir）关于在加沙没有停火且人质被扣押的情况下不开放以色列馆的标语本身已成为一种装置。另外，贝埃里基布兹的一个独特的客座项目以及为什么以色列人在这个可怕的时代阅读更多的恐怖小说</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 19:49:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/actually-there-is-an-israeli-exhibit-at-the-venice-biennale/0000018e-f153-ddac-a59e-f9db55e90000</guid></item><item><title>“我被教导种族灭绝永远不应该再次发生”：吉尔斯坦诉以色列国</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/i-was-taught-genocide-should-never-happen-again-jill-stein-vs-the-state-of-israel/0000018e-f28f-dea6-ab9e-f28f095d0000</link><description>在2016年美国总统选举中，吉尔·斯坦作为绿党候选人获得了150万张选票，削弱了希拉里·克林顿的实力，甚至可能帮助唐纳德·特朗普赢得了胜利。今天，她的民调支持率为 4%，她可能会再次成为剧透。但现在，10 月 7 日之后，哈佛犹太医生的战斗口号是对抗以色列</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 19:35:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/i-was-taught-genocide-should-never-happen-again-jill-stein-vs-the-state-of-israel/0000018e-f28f-dea6-ab9e-f28f095d0000</guid></item><item><title>谷歌因抗议公司与以色列的交易而解雇了 28 名员工</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/google-fires-28-employees-after-protesting-against-companys-deal-with-israel/0000018e-f204-daad-a3de-fe3ff3740000</link><description>抗议活动是由一个名为“No Tech for Apartheid”的组织组织的，该组织的成员在现场告诉记者，他们反对 Nimbus 项目——谷歌和亚马逊于 2021 年获得价值 12 亿美元的合同，为以色列政府提供云计算服务</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 19:24:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-18/ty-article/.premium/google-fires-28-employees-after-protesting-against-companys-deal-with-israel/0000018e-f204-daad-a3de-fe3ff3740000</guid></item><item><title>为什么一段加沙人在海滩上疯传的视频让以色列人抓狂</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-04-18/ty-article/.highlight/why-a-viral-video-of-gazans-at-the-beach-is-driving-israelis-mad/0000018e-f213-d620-abaf-f273f7fc0000</link><description>一张图片可能抵得上一千个字，但在当今社交媒体和 24 小时新闻循环、真相被叙述所取代的时代，这一千个字有很多——太多了——版本</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 19:17:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-04-18/ty-article/.highlight/why-a-viral-video-of-gazans-at-the-beach-is-driving-israelis-mad/0000018e-f213-d620-abaf-f273f7fc0000</guid></item></channel></rss>